 English translation of #日本核废水排海跟踪# 【Important Notice: The key point in the future days for Japan's nuclear wastewater discharge into the sea will come soon】
1. According to reports, the pipeline transporting nuclear waste to the Pacific Ocean has been completed and is expected to obtain safety approval as early as this week;
2. Director-General Rafael Grossi of the International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) will visit Japan starting from Tuesday;
3. The Japanese government expects that the discharge of nuclear wastewater into the ocean will begin this summer, but the specific time has not yet been announced. http://t.cn/A6pgVrXi #日本核废水排海跟踪#【Foreign Ministry: Again warn Japan to stop forcing forward the plan to discharge nuclear-polluted water into the sea】
